| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0519 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ed67dd39-07d1-5ac3-b1ad-aac86c994169"
